KT1LN4LPSqTMS7Sd2CJw4bbDGRkMv2t68Fy9.description: USDtez (USDtz) is the first USD-pegged stablecoin and first FIAT-pegged stablecoin on Tezos. It is backed 1-1 with FIAT, keeping full and transparent reserves and enabling a secure, scalable, and [financial instrument] programmable source of liquidity. USDtez is an open-source project built by multiple firms in the Tezos ecosystem, and is coordinated by Tezos Stable Technologies (StableTech) which operates under the aegis of the Tezos Stablecoin Foundation — a non-shareholder foundation.
